  BLANK //state field was left blank
  NA //address is outside USA
  AL
  AK
  AZ
  AR
  CA
  CO
  CT
  DE
  DC
  FL
  GA
  HI
  ID
  IL
  IN
  IA
  KS
  KY
  LA
  ME
  MD
  MA
  MI
  MN
  MS
  MO
  MT
  NE
  NV
  NH
  NJ
  NM
